        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Qu', 3: 'Most machines are too weak to accommodate you, and the other Constructs fail to match your beauty. You are perfection itself. That\\'s why I set up the trade fair and spent night after night, looking for a vessel for you.', 4: '1'}"
